        public static Baseline create(String basename,
                              Component component,
                              File view,
                              Baseline.LabelBehaviour labelBehaviour,
                              boolean identical,
                              List<Activity> activities,
                              List<Component> depends)
                       throws UnableToInitializeEntityException,
                              UnableToCreateEntityException,
                              NothingNewException
        Given a baseline basename, a component and a view, the baseline is created.
        Parameters:
        basename - The base name for the new Baseline
        component - The Component in which the baseline should be created
        view - Current SnapshotView view root.
        labelBehaviour - The Baseline.LabelBehaviour to use.
        identical - Should we allow identical baselines to be created?
        activities - Activities
        depends - Add Component dependencies
        Returns:
        Created baselines with the given arguments
        Throws:
        UnableToInitializeEntityException - Thrown when ClearCase reports errors
        UnableToCreateEntityException - Thrown when ClearCase reports errors
        NothingNewException - Thrown when ClearCase reports errors

      • promote

        public Project.PromotionLevel promote()
                               throws UnableToPromoteBaselineException
        Promote the Baseline.
        • INITIAL to BUILT
        • BUILD to TESTED
        • TESTED to RELEASED
        If the promotion level is not set, it is set to INITAL.
        Returns:
        The new promotion level.
        Throws:
        UnableToPromoteBaselineException - Thrown when ClearCase reports errors
